line-block;min-width:52px;text-align:center;padding:3px 6px;border-radius:5px;font-size:10px;background:#f5f5f5;margin:2px 4px 2px 0;'> Isoterma<br/><b>200 m</b></span><span style='display:inline-block;min-width:52px;text-align:center;padding:3px 6px;border-radius:5px;font-size:10px;background:#f5f5f5;margin:2px 4px 2px 0;'> Temp<br/><b>2.7&deg; a 3.4&deg;C</b></span><span style='display:inline-block;min-width:52px;text-align:center;padding:3px 6px;border-radius:5px;font-size:10px;background:#f5f5f5;margin:2px 4px 2px 0;'> Viento<br/><b>44 km/h</b></span></div></div><small style='color:#888;'>Precip = acumulada por ventana, por modelo. Iso = isoterma 0&deg;C mas baja. Temp = min/max (prom. 3 modelos). Viento = rafaga maxima (peor caso, 10m).</small><br/><br/><hr/><small><b>Umbrales:</b></small><table cellspacing='1' cellpadding='1'><tr><td bgcolor='#00cc00'>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td><small>&nbsp;&lt;5 o iso&lt;2500&nbsp;</small></td><td bgcolor='#cc9900'>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td><small>&nbsp;&ge;5 + iso&ge;2500&nbsp;</small></td><td bgcolor='#ff0000'>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td><small>&nbsp;&ge;20 + iso&ge;3000</small></td></tr></table>]]></description>
